12/30/18🙏🏻 putting this video together really made me tear up. I cherish all of our pictures and videos together because they mean more then anything to me now. this video just shows the soul you have and how supportive and loving you are!! today marks 4 years and it never gets easier. I would do anything to hug you right now like in that first video. There’s not a day that goes by where i don’t think about you and talk to you in my mind. you are my angel and i know you and god are guiding me through this life but i wish you were here in person, it still never feels real to me that you aren’t physically here. today we will honor and celebrate the amazing, beautiful, goofy, loving soul you are like we do everyday!!! you have shaped me into the person i am and i’m so grateful god made you my dad🇮🇹🤘🏻 cheers to the coolest and best dad of all time Danny B🙏🏻❤️🥹😭♾️♾️♾️♾️ Mom, Kylie, and I love you INFINITY! and miss your soul everyday! until we meet again💓 #dannyb #bestdadever #myangel

last week of @thespacetrainingprograms so thankful for all the memories/ guidance this beautiful space has given me!!! @thespacetv

the final week put into a 3 minute and 30 second vlog😭⭐️🖤✨🙏🏼 this vid took so long to make and it’s just a lil glimpse into the final week leading up to our showcase that was so amazing and beautiful!! I don’t wanna make this caption to long but I want to say a huge thank you to my mentors @officialkristamiller / @thinkmillergroup for the past 5 years of guidance, love, training, support, opportunities, and being my cali parents since i was 15 years old!!! it’s been a wildly, amazing, beautiful past 5 years!!! moving all the way to cali from NY at 15 was crazy and i’m so thankful i made this decision because i don’t know where or who i’d be without this experience!!! I am so beyond grateful i literally have no words, even when it got hard at times i always had the support of my family, friends, and mentors to get through it! I know @thespacetv will forever be family and home! i’m so excited for this next chapter of life and to keep living out my dance dreams in LA and making sh*t happen🙏🏼✨ i’ll forever take all i’ve learned from the program with me till the end! SO MUCH LOVE FOR EVERYONE I CANT EVEN EXPLAIN IT!!!!!! it’s never a goodbye and i’ll always be around xoxo🩷🖤🩷🖤⭐️ #launchtrainingprogram #vlog #dancerlife #caligirl #losangeles #bellabruno
